reviewText: The. Best. We love Fanboy & ChumChum - we bought the DVDs before they put it on Netflix, and now that its off - this DVD is back in heavy rotation.
My kids enjoy watching Fanboy and Chum Chum and have had several hours of entertainment.  Worth the purchase price and delivered promptly.

I bought this for my daughter and she loves it!  Yeah, I know, it's silly, but it's funny and the kids love it!  Nickelodeon has another hit on their hands, and it gives the kids something else to watch besides Spongebob.  Don't get me wrong, I like Spongebob, but it's nice to get a break from that show once in awhile!
Funny show! Gift for my daughter, kids love these guys.

This show is stupid! What happened to rugrats and rocko's modern life? Fan boy and cum cum is just trying to be funny, by using fart humor non stop ! Thank God it is canceled ! I mean what kind of theme song would say "I mean look at our underwear"? Obviously, people rating it 5 stars have no sense to humor anymore.
